{"tid":576902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"津巴布韋部長：中國製避孕套尺碼太細　大陸網民：辱華言論","createTime":"2018-03-01T09:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T10:09:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"10a6f7c8a90925af6373c81f44867dcfc0497e45","tid":576902,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/david-10_8Tyl5_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fdavid-10_8Tyl5_1200x0.png&h=2dd6e4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMade in China 貨品傾銷全球會出現咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n津巴布韋衛生部長告訴你，問題可大可小，甚至關乎人命。他日前現身說法，指責中國製避孕套尺碼太細，並鼓勵國內企業「自己 dom dom 自己做」。<br />\n<br />\n根據 New Zimbabwe 報道，津巴布韋計劃成立對抗愛滋病和 HIV 的新項目，衛生部長 David Parirenyatwa 周二重申避孕套是預防性病和避孕的有效方法。以 2016 年為例，分銷當地的避孕套逾 1 億個，平均每個男性每年分得 33 個避孕套。<br />\n<br />\nParirenyatwa 續指，當地大部分避孕套由中國進口，但部分男性投訴中國貨「尺碼太細」。國內年輕人都有自己喜歡的避孕套類型，但無人願意生產，進口產品尺碼又不合用，道：「我哋應該咁諗：我哋有能力擁有自己嘅 condom，所以如果你想做大生意，就應該為呢個地方嘅人生產自己嘅 condom」。<br />\n<br />\n言論一出，即時傷害某民族感情，一地玻璃碎。有網民形容津巴布韋衛生部長發表「辱華言論」，亦有網民問道「說事實是不是不能算辱華？」《南華早報》聯絡到中國一間避孕套生產商，對方表示知悉津巴布韋的意見，積極考慮生產不同尺碼的避孕套。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/津巴布韋部長-中國製避孕套尺碼太細-大陸網民-辱華言論/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%B4%A5%E5%B7%B4%E5%B8%83%E9%9F%8B%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E9%81%BF%E5%AD%95%E5%A5%97%E5%B0%BA%E7%A2%BC%E5%A4%AA%E7%B4%B0-%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E8%BE%B1%E8%8F%AF%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%2F&d=%2FZa3iQc4fltFCp5TNCbeK0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=fda55112\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%B4%A5%E5%B7%B4%E5%B8%83%E9%9F%8B%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E9%81%BF%E5%AD%95%E5%A5%97%E5%B0%BA%E7%A2%BC%E5%A4%AA%E7%B4%B0-%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E8%BE%B1%E8%8F%AF%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%2F&h=8511992c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/津巴布韋部長-中國製避孕套尺碼太細-大陸網民-辱華言論/</a>"},{"pid":"2653c279198d6afbf233c81d0b9d7c931795c738","tid":576902,"uid":170760,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T10:06:33.000Z","msg":"一地玻璃<br />\n麻煩搵姐姐掃一掃，唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d4fba3c858f06b5d66687e28cbe9f2ac028284","tid":576902,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T10:07:43.000Z","msg":"Parirenyatwa 點讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0be713d90093bfb420bf12fcb4ae25ce58f45d0","tid":576902,"uid":48,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"78d4fba3c858f06b5d66687e28cbe9f2ac028284","tid":576902,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T10:07:43.000Z","msg":"Parirenyatwa 點讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T10:09:00.000Z","msg":"In the beninging"}]}